OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChance of a shower at first
OL,6,Fthis morning otherwise dry with some
OL,7,Fsunshine. This afternoon will be dry
OL,8,Fwith sunny intervals. Very warm. but
OL,9,Fsomewhat cooler across County Down.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be largely dry and
OL,14,Fcloudy, a little rain possible across
OL,15,Fthe far west later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FAfter a cloudy start it will
OL,18,Fbe a dry day with plenty of sunshine
OL,19,Fdeveloping by afternoon. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
