OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain spreading east on
OL,7,FMonday, heavy at times. Scattered
OL,8,Fshowers on Sunday. Further rain likely
OL,9,Fon Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
